---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
<div class="welcome-section">
  <h1>欢迎来到【圣光忽悠着你】</h1>
  <blockquote>
    <p>在艾泽拉斯的魔潮之下，圣骑士不是一本正经的布道者，而是高举锤子、带着圣光到处找乐子的乐子人。</p>
    <p>我们把所有严肃的机制拆开、把所有天赋玩出花样、把所有副本变成我们的游乐场。</p>
    <p>圣光忽悠着你，我们也忽悠着圣光。</p>
  </blockquote>
</div>
<style>
  .welcome-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('your-background-image.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    color: #f0c040; /* 圣光金色 */
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
  }
  .welcome-section h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ffd700;
  }
  .welcome-section blockquote {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    border-left: 4px solid #ffd700;
    padding-left: 30px;
  }
  .welcome-section blockquote p {
    margin: 20px 0;
  }
</style>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
